name: Papillon
description:
"In the time before time, some say there was a great darkness. The earth trembled. The sun hid its face. There were flashes of black lightning and the thunder shook the world. And from this dark time, we became who we were always meant to be." - Sykcolo / AI

Papillon by @Sykcoloart

Taking something that most would consider ugly or repulsive and showing it in a different way that transforms it into something uniquely beautiful is the main passion behind this project that I called Metamorphoses.

This artwork is created using generative techniques to mutate and deconstruct a micrograph of a butterfly antennae and eye. 

Learn about the inspiration, story and techniques behind this project on my website: https://www.sykcolo.com/blog-1/the-metamorphoses-collection
